message appears at the top of the window.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="margin: 7.5pt 0in 0.0001pt 21pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:9.0pt;
font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333">Validation passed&nbsp;- the
settings are all valid and the Content Store will display the ITOM Marketplace capsule tiles.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="margin: 7.5pt 0in 0.0001pt 21pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:9.0pt;
