more settings are not valid and the Content Store remains disabled for ITOM Marketplace capsules.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 21pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size:9.0pt;
font-family:&quot;Verdana&quot;,sans-serif;color:#333333">If the validation fails, check
the following:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 39pt; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><ul><li><span style="letter-spacing: 0.2px; text-indent: -0.25in; background-color: transparent; font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">You have access to the internet through the proxy information
you provided.</span></li><li><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt; letter-spacing: 0.2px; text-indent: -0.25in; background-color: transparent;">Your Access Manager credentials are correct.</span></li><li><span style="letter-spacing: 0.2px; text-indent: -0.25in; background-color: transparent; font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">You have permission to access the&nbsp;<span class="productnamescsa">CSA/HCM&nbsp;</span>product page on the&nbsp;<span class="csavariablesitom">ITOM Marketplace</span>.</span></li></ul></p><p style="margin: 7.5pt 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">























